"56:70:5" : {s: 56, a: 70, w: 5, r: "", t: "فَلَوْلَا", l: "لَوْلَآ", lc: 75, tl: "falawla", lb: "যদি না",e: "**then why are you not grateful?", b: "তাই যদি না (হতো)/তবে কেন নয় যে", i: "maka mengapa tidak", f: 13, rm: "", ag: "فاء استئنافية وحرف تحضيض ", eg: "Resumption fa and Exhortation particle ", tag: "EXH", pos: "EXH", att: "", qual: "", deg: "", gen: "", num: "", mood: "", lu: ""},
"56:70:6" : {s: 56, a: 70, w: 6, r: "شكر", t: "تَشْكُرُونَ", l: "شَكَرَ", lc: 46, tl: "tashkurūna", lb: "ধন্যবাদ দেওয়া",e: "then why are you not grateful", b: "কৃতজ্ঞ হও", i: "kamu bersyukur", f: 19, rm: "to give thanks, be grateful, realize or acknowledge ones favour, praise. shukrun - giving thanks, gratitude. shaakirun - one who gives thanks or is grateful, appreciated and bountiful in reward.", ag: "فعل مضارع وضمير متصل ", eg: "Verb Imperfect and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "IMPF", qual: "", deg: "2", gen: "M", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "شَكَرَ،شَكُورٌۭ،شَاكِرٌ،شَٰكِرُونَ،يَشْكُرُ"},
"56:71:1" : {s: 56, a: 71, w: 1, r: "راي", t: "أَفَرَءَيْتُمُ", l: "رَءَا", lc: 271, tl: "afara-aytumu", lb: "(ভেবে/চোখে/স্বপ্ন) দেখা, উপলব্ধি করা",e: "Do you see", b: "তোমারা কি ভেবে দেখেছ?", i: "maka apakah kamu memperhatikan", f: 3, rm: "to see/think/hold, in opinion of, perceive, judge, consider, know. araitaka / araitakum - do tell me thou/you (the personal pronoun ك is added for emphasis and is not purely as pleonism without adding to the meaning). tarani is for a compound word of a verb tara followed by a pronoun ni - you see me. badi al-rayi - having superficial view, outward appearance, first thought, apparently, without proper consideration. rayalain - to see with naked eye, judgement by sight. riyun - outward appearance, make a show. ruya - vision dream. alam tara - behold! lo! riaun - hypocrisy, ostentation, to be seen. taraa - to see one another, consider, come in sight of one another. yurauna - they deceive hypocritically assuming a false appearance.", ag: "الف الاستفهام وفاء زائدة وفعل ماض وضمير متصل ", eg: "Interrogative alif and Supplemental fa and Verb Perfect and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "PERF", qual: "", deg: "2", gen: "M", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "رَءَا،رَأَىٰٓ"},
