"56:74:3" : {s: 56, a: 74, w: 3, r: "ربب", t: "رَبِّكَ", l: "رَبّ", lc: 975, tl: "rabbika", lb: "প্রভু, সযত্নে পালনকর্তা",e: "(of) your Lord", b: "তোমার প্রভুর", i: "Tuhanmu", f: 81, rm: "to be a lord and master, collect, possess/owner, rule, increase, complete, bring up, preserve, chief, guardian, regulator, determiner, caretaker, provider, sustainer, perfecter, rewarder, creator, maintainer, reposer of properties, developer, former of rules and laws of the growth, foster a thing in such a manner as to make it attain one condition after another until it reaches its goal of completion, the bringing a thing to a state of completion by degrees, whoever possesses a thing is its rabb.", ag: "أسم مجرور وضمير متصل ", eg: "Noun Genitive case and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "GEN", qual: "", deg: "", gen: "M", num: "", mood: "", lu: ""},
